Name:		xemacs-frame-icon-pkg
%define 	srcname	frame-icon
Version:	1.09
Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		Applications/Editors/Emacs
Group(pl):	Aplikacje/Edytory/Emacs
Source0:	ftp://ftp.xemacs.org/xemacs/packages/%{srcname}-%{version}-pkg.tar.gz
